headline: Select Billionaire Money Managers Are Selling a Stock-Split Stock That's Gained 214,000% Since Its IPO -- and They're Likely to Regret It
summary: This unstoppable company has split its shares nine times in the last 37 years, but found itself on the chopping block by a pair of billionaire fund managers in the first quarter.
